# ClauseGuard v2 — Build Walkthrough

## What Was Built

A complete AI-powered legal contract analyzer with **React + FastAPI + Ollama**, running 100% locally.

### Backend (Python/FastAPI)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [requirements.txt](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/backend/requirements.txt) | Python dependencies |
| [models.py](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/backend/models.py) | Pydantic data models for Clause and AnalysisResult |
| [pdf_parser.py](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/backend/pdf_parser.py) | PDF text extraction via PyMuPDF |
| [url_scraper.py](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/backend/url_scraper.py) | URL content scraper (requests + BeautifulSoup) |
| [llm_service.py](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/backend/llm_service.py) | Ollama/Mistral integration with JSON cleanup |
| [main.py](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/backend/main.py) | FastAPI app with 3 endpoints: `/analyze/pdf`, `/analyze/url`, `/analyze/text` |

### Frontend (React + Vite + TailwindCSS)

| File | Purpose |
|---|---|
| [App.jsx](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/frontend/src/App.jsx) | Main shell with animated orbs, glassmorphism nav, gradient hero |
| [UploadPanel.jsx](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/frontend/src/components/UploadPanel.jsx) | 3-tab input (PDF drag-drop, URL, text) with gradient analyze button |
| [RiskReport.jsx](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/frontend/src/components/RiskReport.jsx) | Full analysis report with animated risk meter, clause cards |
| [ClauseCard.jsx](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/frontend/src/components/ClauseCard.jsx) | Individual clause display (red for risk, green for safe) |
| [Loader.jsx](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/frontend/src/components/Loader.jsx) | Shield icon + spinner with privacy message |
| [index.css](file:///c:/Users/SUBHAMAY%20RAJ/OneDrive/Desktop/ClauseGuard_h/frontend/src/index.css) | Tailwind + glassmorphism, gradients, scrollbar, glow effects |

