## UI Enhancements Over Brief

- **Animated background orbs** — floating indigo/purple gradient blobs
- **Glassmorphism cards** — `backdrop-blur` + semi-transparent backgrounds
- **Gradient branding** — indigo-to-purple gradient on "ClauseGuard" and "contract."
- **Drag-and-drop** PDF upload with visual feedback
- **Micro-animations** — hover lift, tab transitions, staggered report sections
- **Risk meter glow** — colored glow matching risk level
- **Inter font** — premium typography from Google Fonts
- **Custom scrollbar** — styled to match theme

