## How to Run

```bash
# Terminal 1 — Ollama (must be running first)
ollama serve

# Terminal 2 — Backend
cd backend
.\venv\Scripts\activate
uvicorn main:app --reload --port 8000

# Terminal 3 — Frontend
cd frontend
npm run dev
# Open http://localhost:5173
```
